</ul>
</li>
<li>두 query는 동일하지는 않지만, <strong>동등</strong>함
<ul>
<li>어떤 데이터베이스에서도 동일한 결과를 제공하기 때문.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="modification-of-the-database" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#modification-of-the-database"><span>Modification of the Database</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>데이터베이스의 내용은 다음 연산들을 사용하여 <strong>수정</strong>될 수 있음:
<ul>
<li>Deletion</li>
<li>Insertion</li>
<li>Updating</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>이 모든 연산은 <strong>assignment</strong> 연산자를 사용하여 표현됨</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="deletion" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#deletion"><span>Deletion</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>Delete(삭제) 요청은 query와 유사하게 표현되지만, 사용자에게 tuple을 표시하는 대신 선택된 tuple이 데이터베이스에서 제거됨</li>
<li>전체 tuple만 삭제 가능. 특정 attributes의 값만 삭제 불가</li>
<li>Deletion은 relational algebra에서 다음과 같이 표현됨: <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mo>←</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r \leftarrow r - E</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span>
<ul>
<li>여기서 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span></span></span></span>은 relation이고 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span>는 relational algebra query</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>예시)
<ul>
<li>Perryridge 지점의 모든 계좌 기록 삭제: <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mtext>account</mtext><mo>←</mo><mtext>account</mtext><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>σ</mi><mrow><mi>b</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>h</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>e</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext>“</mtext><mi>P</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>y</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>e</mi><mtext>”</mtext></mrow></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>account</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{account} \leftarrow \text{account} - \sigma_{branch-name = “Perryridge”}(\text{account})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6151em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">account</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6984em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">account</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0361em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">σ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">b</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">an</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">c</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">h</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">nam</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">e</span><span class="mrel mtight">=</span><span class="mord mtight">“</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">erryr</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">e</span><span class="mord mtight">”</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">account</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></li>
<li>금액이 <code v-pre>0</code>에서 <code v-pre>50</code> 사이인 모든 대출 기록 삭제: <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mtext>loan</mtext><mo>←</mo><mtext>loan</mtext><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>σ</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>∧</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>50</mn></mrow></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>loan</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{loan} \leftarrow \text{loan} - \sigma_{amount \geq 0 \land amount \leq 50}(\text{loan})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">loan</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7778em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">loan</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">σ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">am</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">u</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">n</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">t</span><span class="mrel mtight">≥</span><span class="mord mtight">0</span><span class="mbin mtight">∧</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">am</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">u</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">n</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">t</span><span class="mrel mtight">≤</span><span class="mord mtight">50</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2452em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">loan</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="insertion" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#insertion"><span>Insertion</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>Relation에 데이터를 삽입하기 위해:
<ul>
<li>삽입할 tuple을 명시하거나</li>
<li>결과가 삽입될 tuple들의 집합인 query를 작성</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Relational algebra에서 insertion은 다음과 같이 표현됨: <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mo>←</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>∪</mo><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r \leftarrow r \cup E</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5556em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∪</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span>
<ul>
<li>여기서 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span></span></span></span>은 relation이고 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span>는 relational algebra expression</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>단일 tuple의 삽입은 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span>를 하나의 tuple을 포함하는 상수 relation으로 하여 표현됨</li>
<li>예:
<ul>
<li><code v-pre>Smith</code>가 <code v-pre>Perryridge</code> 지점의 <code v-pre>A-973</code> 계좌에 <code v-pre>$1200</code>를 가지고 있다는 정보를 데이터베이스에 삽입</li>
<li><span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mtext>account</mtext><mo>←</mo><mtext>account</mtext><mo>∪</mo><mtext>(&quot;Perryridge&quot;, A-973, 1200)</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{account} \leftarrow \text{account} \cup \text{(&quot;Perryridge&quot;, A-973, 1200)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6151em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">account</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6151em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">account</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∪</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">(&quot;Perryridge&quot;, A-973, 1200)</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mtext>depositor</mtext><mo>←</mo><mtext>depositor</mtext><mo>∪</mo><mtext>(&quot;Smith&quot;, A-973)</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{depositor} \leftarrow \text{depositor} \cup \text{(&quot;Smith&quot;, A-973)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">depositor</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">depositor</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∪</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">(&quot;Smith&quot;, A-973)</span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="updating" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#updating"><span>Updating</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Tuple의 모든 값을 변경하지 않고 tuple의 값을 변경하는 메커니즘</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>이 작업을 수행하기 위해 generalized projection operator(일반화된 프로젝션 연산자)를 사용</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mo>←</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Π</mi><mrow><msub><mi>F</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>F</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>F</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></mrow></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r \leftarrow \Pi_{F_1, F_2, ..., F_n}(r)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0361em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">Π</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3173em;"><span style="top:-2.357em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.0714em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.143em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct mtight">,</span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3173em;"><span style="top:-2.357em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.0714em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.143em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct mtight">,</span><span class="mord mtight">...</span><span class="mpunct mtight">,</span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1645em;"><span style="top:-2.357em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.0714em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">n</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.143em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>각 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>F</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>는,</p>
<ul>
<li>i번째 attribute가 업데이트되지 않으면 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span></span></span></span>의 i번째 attribute이거나,</li>
<li>만약 attribute가 업데이트되어야 한다면, <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>F</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>는 상수와 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span></span></span></span>의 attributes만을 포함하는 expression으로, attribute의 <strong>새로운 값</strong>을 제공</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>예:</p>
<ul>
<li>모든 잔액을 5% 증가시켜 이자 지급하기</li>
</ul>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mtext>account</mtext><mo>←</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Π</mi><mtext>AN, BN, BAL * 1.05</mtext></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>account</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{account} \leftarrow \Pi_\text{AN, BN, BAL * 1.05}(\text{account})
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6151em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">account</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">←</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0663em;vertical-align:-0.3163em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">Π</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3448em;"><span style="top:-2.5198em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord text mtight"><span class="mord mtight">AN, BN, BAL * 1.05</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3163em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">account</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li>여기서 <code v-pre>AN</code>, <code v-pre>BN</code>, <code v-pre>BAL은</code> 각각 <code v-pre>account-number</code>, <code v-pre>branch-name</code>, <code v-pre>balance</code>를 의미</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
